{"tid":2032071,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"t寶新單曲〈Fanfare〉七月發行 全員散發滿滿 果！汁！美！ ^_^","createTime":"2020-05-23T22:59:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T03:26:57.000Z","uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dc9bd26022ff8c0b8baf25cce226d0aca5564ee2","tid":2032071,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T22:59:31.000Z","msg":"即將在6月1日回歸，第九張迷你專輯《MORE &amp; MORE》的回歸宣傳也如火如荼進行著，包括先前陸續釋出的形象照、概念影片、專輯配置等等，每每有新消息傳出，讓粉絲們的期待值再度往上升。而官方在本月五日宣布了好消息，那就是第七張日文單曲〈Fanfare〉即將在7月8日發行，今天官方也釋出首波概念照，跟《MORE &amp; MORE》同樣有著濃濃夏季感，成員們個個散發果汁美，整體造型非常青春洋溢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/05/22/99/7916926.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F05%2F22%2F99%2F7916926.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D750&h=5b481a10&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"805689fb99e614e94cfff1254fbd267108ea26e8","tid":2032071,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T22:59:42.000Z","msg":"〈Fanfare〉是繼去年七月的〈Breakthrough〉後的第七張日文單曲。不管是《MORE &amp; MORE》或是〈Fanfare〉的形象風格，都跟去年的《Feel Special》成熟風截然不同。因應夏季女團大戰，此次的風格則是走一個健康、甜美、陽光的路線。今天釋出的主視覺中，成員們換上潔白的上衣及白鞋，在牆上揮灑著絢爛繽紛的色彩。髮色皆以新造型亮相，成員們不只臉上，就連身上也沾染了顏料，非常有青春的氛圍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/05/22/99/7916930.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F05%2F22%2F99%2F7916930.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D750&h=8e111177&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c72976a3c678fe858bbd5385f64a30a4228003d0","tid":2032071,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T22:59:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/05/22/99/7916931.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F05%2F22%2F99%2F7916931.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D750&h=0399ec95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/05/22/99/7916932.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F05%2F22%2F99%2F7916932.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D750&h=4e71ecf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外兩張則宛如「威力在哪裡」般的構圖，她們換上各種造型，手上拿著各式各樣的道具，彷彿大家來找碴，考考ONCE們的眼力，來找找你最喜歡的成員。接著，官方也釋出了成員個人照，即使臉上沾著顏料，但成員們的美貌依舊無懈可擊！每一張都想按下右鍵收藏！"},{"pid":"f0a8e805c93e3e0438929c31a9d9c84649293d60","tid":2032071,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T23:00:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/05/22/99/7916933.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F05%2F22%2F99%2F7916933.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D750&h=c3f91110&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f97d3bbeecf3da45dd3891336ce2c85873d801c8","tid":2032071,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T23:00:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/05/22/99/7916940.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.co